		"short-abstract": "There is growing interest in running Apache Spark natively on Kubernetes (see https://github.com/apache-spark-on-k8s/spark). Spark applications often access data in HDFS, and Spark supports HDFS locality by scheduling tasks on nodes that have the task input data on their local disks. ",
